Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.50,0:01:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(康斯肯的強襲)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.40,0:01:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前，曾經是\N衛星一號的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.67,0:02:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在，卻成了薩比家中將
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.51,0:02:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所指揮的宇宙攻擊總部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.41,0:02:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙要塞-所羅門基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.19,0:02:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裡，康斯肯的部隊\N剛剛出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德茲爾中將對姊姊希莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.77,0:02:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再次任用夏亞\N感到非常的反感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他很想自己來擊沉母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.21,0:02:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,籍以証明夏亞的無能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.54,0:02:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他們仍未查明\N帝姆艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.78,0:02:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去月神二號的目的前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.08,0:02:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不能派遺\N太多兵力去別處的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.03,0:02:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，妳覺得怎樣？\N有不妥當嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.60,0:03:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照看應是沒問題的\N不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.97,0:03:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這附近有很多岩石\N便很難說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.71,0:03:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱，你聽到嗎？怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.34,0:03:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切正常\N不過我不能長途飛行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是先回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.65,0:03:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想G戰機再巡一次\N可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.75,0:03:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那對我來說\N可以做多些飛行練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？阿姆羅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認為芙勞‧波的為人怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.86,0:03:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？為何妳會這樣問？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.36,0:03:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.53,0:03:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你最近對她很冷淡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.40,0:03:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有這種事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得是有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.87,0:03:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為這時最重要是友誼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.67,0:03:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我沒有\N說過討厭她呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有敵軍！         咦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照情況看是被發現了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，再等一會吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若不是故障\N不會被發現的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.56,0:03:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引擎沒問題吧！   沒事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.24,0:04:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了，雪拉快閃開！   咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.98,0:04:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們開火了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吉翁的機動堡壘嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.95,0:04:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...還是未知道的！\N又來了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.75,0:04:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈有此理，為何開火啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他們想攻擊我們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.52,0:04:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們根本\N就沒有攻擊的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.89,0:04:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太沒膽了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！這架戰機看來很快速！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.53,0:04:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們分開作戰\N快閃到岩石後！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.21,0:04:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們將電力加得太高了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.64,0:04:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法了\N既然已暴露了行蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.54,0:04:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯有拚死一戰了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.95,0:04:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3...2...1...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.56,0:05:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裡呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.36,0:05:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是一架戰機\N不用怕的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.17,0:05:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們以很高速攻過來了\N小心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們到底\N從那裡攻擊過來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎是多方向呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.52,0:05:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.73,0:05:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼辛苦才修理好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.54,0:05:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，很久了\N進入衛星六號前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先返回母艦吧！   知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這燈塔後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.22,0:06:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便是衛星六號領空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.89,0:06:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是聯邦或吉翁也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.99,0:06:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一律是被禁止\N在這裡開戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.34,0:06:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是衛星六號的檢查官\N卡姆蘭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.92,0:06:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經在母艦的\N導彈發射口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.98,0:06:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大炮，雷射炮\N用這樣封條封好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.22,0:06:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既使你們弄破了一條\N也知道的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.09,0:06:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了，會罰巨款是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.96,0:06:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想修理母艦\N可以幫忙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這...也不可以\N在衛星內進行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.93,0:06:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這等於協助戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.44,0:06:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帶你控制室看看\N好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.34,0:07:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呢，雪拉\N我明明看得清徹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那炮火不是在\N戰機的方向射過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.88,0:07:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不會看錯的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.55,0:07:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還未查出原因嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看那是新型的機動堡壘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.39,0:07:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能的         是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.36,0:07:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來得剛好\N我們正要入港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.36,0:07:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入港角度好，速度0.5
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在進入衛星六號\N巴達港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.70,0:07:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請各位做好準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,角度360
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開所有雷射調整器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊？妳不是米萊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.42,0:07:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆蘭，是你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.99,0:07:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，妳沒有事\N真太好了...米萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.69,0:07:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看來很精神，你好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是誰？         或許是親人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.10,0:07:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆蘭檢察官\N現在正要入港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以待會再說嗎？\N米萊少尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.94,0:08:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀...中尉，對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.64,0:08:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很高興的呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為再見不到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以為沒希望了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.34,0:08:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全因為妳父親過世後...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則便不會有戰爭了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.58,0:08:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，否則\N我也不會去移民去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SIDE 7裡，逃避事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.52,0:08:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因為這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.66,0:08:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳為什麼不通知我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很想得到妳的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.36,0:08:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經盡力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡了力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.36,0:09:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀！我著人四處去找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.36,0:09:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用盡了所有的金錢！\N是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.67,0:09:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...為何你\N不自己來找呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.54,0:09:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我已申請了\N來衛星六號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這門親事\N由於是父母作主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.48,0:09:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才會這樣說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.15,0:09:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的，米萊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.82,0:09:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳誤會了\N請來舍下坐坐吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.92,0:09:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦...但是...\N我父親會很開心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.56,0:09:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了妳\N我什麼也願意做的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.19,0:09:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等！         對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家不喜歡\N別勉強好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史列加中尉，不要緊的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.54,0:09:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的？         是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.01,0:09:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔...算你走運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.18,0:09:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接住自己的眼鏡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.95,0:09:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧，卡姆蘭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.92,0:09:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能我的說服力不夠呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.19,0:10:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎，中尉\N你要小心才好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.53,0:10:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要知道\N米萊是母艦的褓姆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說你最先\N是德茲爾中將的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現在卻是\N希莉亞少將的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.67,0:10:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不覺得羞恥的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底給木馬號\N走脫了多少次？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.61,0:10:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是無能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.82,0:10:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你好好看著我的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底如何高明！      是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰說你可以走的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你別太過份！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.63,0:10:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的作戰方法\N我會留心看的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.83,0:10:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙為何\N不脫下面罩的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽他額上有一處疤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有說是個美男子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.97,0:10:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總有一天\N我會脫下他的假面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些潛入\N巴達港多姆如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.84,0:10:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，仍未被發現呢！\N一切很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬亞，你待會回去後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.66,0:11:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就發暗號給希莉亞少將\N是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.89,0:11:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞在巴達內，知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.33,0:11:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是這種小事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別問那麼多，照做吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.54,0:11:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木村先生\N你已換了錢嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.94,0:11:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.98,0:11:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡，是太空城市的中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.38,0:11:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個令人覺得\N無重力的地帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.85,0:11:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這條電梯，約有三千米長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.35,0:11:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐在下面\N就會有地心吸力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.63,0:11:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有重力的人造地面\N山，森林和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.96,0:11:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,河流，與地球上的景色\N完全一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然，亦有人造城市了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.57,0:11:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好，買了很多東西呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次吃的\N比以前豐富多了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.59,0:12:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.87,0:12:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣，阿姆羅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.34,0:12:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們先回母艦吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我過去那間書店看看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.03,0:12:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.04,0:13:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.86,0:13:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.74,0:13:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈的作戰成績怎樣？\N順利嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.44,0:13:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔！跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還站著幹什麼？\N快進來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.79,0:13:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.72,0:13:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是下層階級住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過在這裡\N收集情報很方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.03,0:14:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才會寄住在這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.70,0:14:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你將它放在\N鋼彈的記錄線路裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些是我計算\N吉翁MS來參考的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.04,0:14:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種舊東西...爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.88,0:14:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來爸爸\N患了缺乏氧氣病...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.85,0:14:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它很利害的\N鋼彈的作戰能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以增加數倍呢！\N快拿回去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡快裝在鋼彈試試吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.95,0:14:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！但是爸爸你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.39,0:14:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還有很多研究課題...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遲些再聯絡你吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.86,0:14:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了，快回母艦去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.77,0:14:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，我在鄉下\N見過媽媽呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.57,0:14:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，媽媽的事\N難道你不關心嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.88,0:14:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔...戰爭快結束了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們將可返回地球...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.72,0:14:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.42,0:15:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回去吧！\N你現在已是個軍人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，我何時\N批准你一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.02,0:15:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在街上四處走的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.02,0:15:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了你，連出發也延遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.42,0:15:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！我想不到\N會突然出發的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.52,0:15:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你用鋼彈\N去掩護白色基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.23,0:15:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是巴金先生嗎？是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.87,0:15:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你是卡姆蘭\N請來幫忙的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.97,0:15:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！是他從首相處\N打電話給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.38,0:15:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要在領空以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.25,0:15:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是吉翁或聯邦的戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也一樣修理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在敵軍正跟蹤我們\N沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...這不要緊的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.22,0:16:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和他們的高層人物\N很熟絡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.66,0:16:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐，請妳即管放心吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝了，巴金先生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.86,0:16:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，精神好點了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.50,0:16:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直也沒事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.90,0:16:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎，那便好了\N乖孩子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.07,0:16:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史列加先生！      什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.84,0:16:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖孩子這句話\N請別再對我說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，是我不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.02,0:16:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了\N那不是木馬號嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.39,0:16:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然這麼傻走來這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那便是流動船塢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔？是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.08,0:17:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說有信號來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.55,0:17:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是母艦駛出\N衛星六號的訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先確定位置\N然後開動引擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.32,0:17:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼木馬號\N會這麼快出來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.49,0:17:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明瞭！是流動船塢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.49,0:17:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說是巴金嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.06,0:17:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是否那個在戰爭中\N賺大錢的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.50,0:17:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們艦隊和敵人\N就成一直線了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.60,0:17:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即刻派出十二台多姆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.18,0:17:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們已經找到木馬號嗎？\N是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.02,0:17:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還派出了多姆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.90,0:17:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很大啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.87,0:17:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了，原來是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.01,0:18:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...我的船塢...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特！我知卡姆蘭\N不是這種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.91,0:18:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部炮門打開吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.71,0:18:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！各單位注意\N立即展開攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.48,0:18:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉...請離開船塢\N遠一點好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.62,0:18:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若這樣下去\N我的船塢會完的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正在離開了...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是有裙的那一種！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.07,0:18:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個，再來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.35,0:18:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標是中間的戰艦！\N攻擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姆沙艦被毀了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.04,0:19:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多姆呢？\N多姆到底在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.31,0:19:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可放鬆攻擊啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.68,0:19:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流動船塢就是在附近嗎？\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.02,0:19:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼吉翁會發現的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.49,0:19:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要停止戰爭的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.32,0:19:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些炮火是不可\N進入衛星領空的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.17,0:19:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,六個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.85,0:19:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.93,0:20:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.48,0:20:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,九個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.05,0:20:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全滅？十二個多姆\N全沒有了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是在三分鐘之內？是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.56,0:20:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一艘已受傷的戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.53,0:20:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將十二台多姆\N全部毀滅了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.70,0:20:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是怪物嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.17,0:20:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贊斯巴爾來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.17,0:20:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞？你是想來笑我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.51,0:20:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贊斯巴爾！         甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.61,0:20:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特\N我們不如先回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.38,0:21:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！全艦注意\N返回衛星六號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.95,0:21:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我的船塢怎辦？怎辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.03,0:21:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千萬別開火\N有監察船在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.70,0:21:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫康斯肯部隊停止攻擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.00,0:21:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若損壞了巡邏艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.37,0:21:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會演變成國際問題的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.47,0:21:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡姆蘭檢察官！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.81,0:21:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有勇氣\N去叫他們停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.65,0:21:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.38,0:21:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過在聯邦軍戰艦內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.38,0:21:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正有我的未婚妻\N米萊在內呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.93,0:21:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊的\N關於撕破封條的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.56,0:21:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸爸會想方法的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.97,0:21:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以借爸爸的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.97,0:21:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫妳們留在衛星六號的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.18,0:22:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是這個意思...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.01,0:22:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要求我離開母艦，但...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.65,0:22:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...你會為我\N做什麼事呢？
